::DarkMouse/KitKat/Shadow Wing::

DarkMouse:: 
She held her head with one hand and looked about.  Her vision was a 
little blurred. "Quickstrike?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

KitKat::
She opened her eyes for a moment.  She saw that she was off the 
ground, flying.  She thought she was on her way to join the Matrix.  
Then she got a glimps of a red wing, "Terrorsaur" she thought.  Then 
she slipped into unconsiousness.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Shadow Wing::
She called on her comlink again. "This is Shadow Wing.  I copy you.  
I need to know roughly where you are so I can help you."

(She is trying to call Silverbolt.)
